'''Kigali'''

Mu buryo budashidikanywaho biherereye mu cyerekezo cy’u Rwanda, Kigali agera hakurya y’imisozi miremire, hamwe n’umuhanda munini uhuza ibisigaye mu gihugu. Umurwa mukuru wuzuye utuje biratuje ariko birakomeye kandi biringaniye, hamwe nabantu barenga gato 1.000.000.

Abashyitsi bwa mbere gutaka no kwibanda cyane bahora batanga ibitekerezo byukuntu umuhanda usukuye, ikibazo cyicyubahiro muri buri gace kanyuze mugihugu.

Muri rusange Kigali ni umujyi mushya. Yashinzwe nka sitasiyo yubuyobozi mu 1907, ihinduka umurwa mukuru wigihugu mu bwigenge mu 1962, yimukira ahitwa Huye.

Ikwirakwizwa ryinshi ryibiti bitondekanye nibiti hamwe na kare byuzuye birinzwe kugenda, aho abirukanwa usanga igice kinini cyanyujijwe kubikoresho byabo usibye niba bakeneye ubufasha, muribwo bazakirwa neza mubaturanyi.

Hano haribintu byagutse byubukorikori, nkumubare witerambere uhitamo kurya hanze no kugira ibinyobwa bibiri, byinshi hamwe no gushuka ibintu byose bikubiyemo. Umudugudu wumuco wa Kigali utanga umwanya wihariye kubanyabukorikori hafi n’abagurisha ibiryo kugirango berekane kandi bahana ibicuruzwa byabo.

Kigali ikura vuba, hamwe na santeri nshya zubucuruzi, ahakorerwa ubucuruzi hamwe na salle yo hejuru yateranirizwagamo ikora muburyo bwingoro yumwami yumunsi wa kera, imurikira ikirere nijoro kuri kamwe mubantu benshi.

'''Masterpiece Mall'''
